enum MmCallState
 

This enumeration comprises types of MmCallEvents.

See also:
MmCallStatusMsg.
Enumerator:
CalledPartyAlerting  An MOC is in setup and the called party is notified.
MtcReady  A MTC was accepted and the call is ready.
MtcArrived  A AT+CRING:MM was detected.
MmCallReleased  An Mm call was released (MTC or MOC).
MmCallOnHold  An active call was switched to hold.
MmCallDisconnecting  A call disconnection is ongoing.
MmCallDisconnectingByUser  A call disconnection initiated by the user is ongoing.
MmCallDisconnectingByNetwork  A call disconnection caused by the network or B-PArty is ongoing.
MmCallDisconnected  A call disconnection is finished.
MmCallDisconnectedByUser  A call disconnection initiated by the user is finished.
MmCallDisconnectedByNetwork  A call disconnection caused by the network or B-PArty is finished.
MmMocSetupAccept  Setting up an MOC is allowed.
MmMocInSetup  A MOC is in setup state.
MmCallProgressIndication  Call establishment progress has occured.
SetupConfirmation  Needed for confirmation that setup has been started.
AcceptConfirmation  Needed for confirmation that accepting the call has been started.
